\id JUD
\ide UTF-8
\h Judi
\toc1 Judi
\toc2 Judi
\toc3 jud
\mt1 Judi
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Judi, mulanda wa Jesu Kkilisito amunyina wa Jemusi, kuli baabo bayitidwe, bayandwa muli Leza Taata babikidwe akaambo ka Jesu Kkilisito.
\v 2 Luse aluumuno aluyando aluvuzigwe kuli ndinywe.
\v 3 Nibayandwa, kandichili kubika nguzu zyoonse kumulembela aatala alufutuko luzibikene, ndakaba akumulembela nywebo kandimusumpula kuti mukakatile loko lusyomo lwakaabilwa boonse bantu ba Leza basalala.
\v 4 kuli bakanjila chakusisikana aakati kan. Aaba mbaalumi bakalitandidwe ankaambo kalubeteko. Mbaalumi batakwe buleza bakasandula luzyalo lwa Lesu wesu akuba azisusi zibi, aabo bakaka simalelo a Mwami, Jesu Kkilisito.
\v 5 Lino ndayanda kumuyeezya - nikuba mwakalizi loko - kuti Leza wakafutula bantu kuzwa munyika ya Igiputi pesi aampela wakabamwayisya aabo abakatazunina.
\v 6 Alubo, baangelo batakwe bakabamba chuuno chabwendelezi, pesi aabo bakasya busena bwabo bulikabotu bwakukkala - Leza wakabamba kuzyaanzyo zitamani, akunjila mumudima, walubeteko lwazuba bupati.
\v 7 Aboobo, Sodoma a Gomola amadolopo azisi zyengeelede aakati kabo balinjizya beni mumamambi anchinto zyabumambi aabo balabeleka mbuli chitondeezyo chabaabo bapenzengwa aachisubulo chamililo utamani.
\v 8 Munzila ikozyene aaba basikulota alabo bakasofwaazya mibili yabo. balakaka bwami akusampawula aabo bali aabulemu.
\v 9 Nikuba alakwe Mayikkelo mwaangelo mupati, nibakali kukazyana a Satani akunyanzyana anguwe munta wa Mozesi, takakonzya kweeta lubeteko aatala anguwe, pesi wati, “Akukalalile Mwami!”
\v 10 Pesi bantu aaba balasampawula kufumbwa nchibatamvwi; anzibamvwa zyabube buliwo, mbuli banyama batayeeyi, eezi nzenzizyo zyakabamwaya.
\v 11 Maawe kuli mbabo!” Nkaambo bayeenda munzila ya Kkayini akunjizigwa mukubisya kwa Bbalamu ankaambo kampindu, balafwa mulupapilo lwa Kkola
\v 12 Aaba bantu mabwe ajeeya kumapobwe aluyando, kupobola andinywe chifwisya bweeme -beembeli balisanina beni. Mayoba atakwe mvula aabwezegwa aaluuwo; misamu yakulwaka itakwe michelo - bafwide tubili banonkwedwe.
\v 13 Mayuwe ali aabukali amulwizi, akubumba bubi, inyenyeezi ziya bwendeende, babambilidwe kusiya kwamudima mawuse kwalyoonse.
\v 14 Inoki mwana wamusaanu kuli Adamu, wakasinsima aatala ambabo, wakati, “Bona! Mwami ulasika azyuulu azyuulu zyabasalali bakwe uzosika kuzoopa lubeta kuli boonse.
\v 15 Uzoosika kuzoopa luteko luli boonse. uyoosika kuzooyumununa zyoonse zitali zyabuleza akumilimu njibakachita munzila ityaliyabuleza akumajwi akumajwim woonse ankondo atakwe aatakwe buleza kuli basizibi nzibaakamba aatala anguwe.”
\v 16 Aaba mbasikunyontooka abasikutongawuka mukutobela zbi zyabo. Milomo yabo ilaambulisya chakulikankayizya, impuwo zyabpo kukasya bamwi.
\v 17 Pesi nubayandwa amuyeeye majwi akaambwa kuchiindi aba apositoli ba Mwami wesu Jesu Kkilisito.
\v 18 Bakati kuli ndinywe, “Kuchiindi chakumamanino kuyooba basikunoonga batobela miyeeyo yabo itali yabuleza
\v 19 .“Abaa mbaaba bachita kwanzyanya; mbaasinyika alubo tabakwe muuya.
\v 20 Pesi nywebo, nobayandwa, amusime lwanu mulusyomo lupati lusalala, akukomba mu Muuya Uusalala.
\v 21 Amukkale muluyando lwa Leza, akulinda luse lwa Mwami Jesu Kkilisitu weeta buumi butamani.
\v 22 Amube aaluse kuli baabo batasyomi.
\v 23 Futula bamwi akubagwisya kuzwa mumulilo. Kuli bamwi amube aaluse lwakuyoowa. Choonzyo nikuba chisamo chasofwazigwa amubili.
\v 24 Lino kuliyooyo umukasya kuzwa mukuwa amukuchita kuti mwiimikile kunembo lyabulemu bwabuliwo butakwe bubi mbubakwaamba alukondo lupati,
\v 25 kuli Leza luzutu mufutuli wesu mukwiinda muli Jesu Kkilisito Mwami wesu, akube bulemu, bupati anguzu, abwami, zyiindi zyoonse zyakaliwo, lino akwalyoonse. Amen. 
